{"kanda":6,"sarga":36,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"तत्तुमाल्यवतोवाक्यंहितमुक्तंदशाननः ।नमर्षयतिदुष्टात्माकालस्यवशमागतः","trans":"The tenheaded Ravana, having fallen under the sway of death could not tolerate Malyavatha's words of advice.","words":[{"d":"दुष्टात्मा","m":"evil minded"},{"d":"दशाननः","m":"the tenheaded"},{"d":"कालस्य","m":"death 's"},{"d":"वशम्","m":"fallen under the sway"},{"d":"आगतः","m":"come"},{"d":"माल्यवतः","m":"Malyavatha"},{"d":"उक्तम्","m":"told"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words of advice"},{"d":"नमर्षयति","m":"not tolerated."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"नबद् ध्वाभ्रुकुटींवक्त्रेक्रोधस्यवशमागतः ।अमर्षात्परिवृत्ताक्षोमाल्यवन्तमथाब्रवीत्","trans":"Then Ravana who had come under the influence of anger, knitting the brows of his face rolling his eyes said to Malyavan.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"क्रोधस्य","m":"by anger"},{"d":"वशम्","m":"submitted to"},{"d":"आगतः","m":"come under"},{"d":"वक्त्रे","m":"in the face"},{"d":"भ्रुकुटिम्","m":"eyebrows"},{"d":"बद् ध्वा","m":"knitting"},{"d":"अमर्षात्","m":"intolerant"},{"d":"परिवृत्ताक्षः","m":"rolling his eyes"},{"d":"अथ","m":"and then"},{"d":"माल्यवन्तम्","m":"to Malyavan"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"said."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"हितबुध्यायदहितंवचःपरुषमुच्यते ।परपक्षंप्रनिश्यैवनैतच्च्रोत्रगतंमम","trans":"\"Harsh and not wellmeaning words have been uttered by you taking the enemy's side. I will not listen to what you said earlier.\"","words":[{"d":"परपक्षम्","m":"enemies side"},{"d":"प्रविश्यैव","m":"taking"},{"d":"हितबुध्या","m":"salutary sense"},{"d":"यत्","m":"those"},{"d":"परुषम्","m":"harsh"},{"d":"अहितम्","m":"not meaning good"},{"d":"वचः","m":"words"},{"d":"उच्यते","m":"have uttered"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"all these"},{"d":"मम","m":"to me"},{"d":"श्रोत्रगतम्","m":"listen to what was told earlier"},{"d":"न","m":"not."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"मानुषंकृपणंराममेकंशाखामृगाश्रयम् ।समर्थंमन्यसेकेनत्यक्तंपित्रावनालयम्","trans":"\"For what reason do you say that a wretched human being, alone, forsaken by a father who has taken asylum in the forest, who is taking the help of vanaras is capable?\"","words":[{"d":"मानुषम्","m":"human"},{"d":"कृपणम्","m":"wretched"},{"d":"एकम्","m":"alone"},{"d":"शाखामृगाश्रयम्","m":"who has the help of herbivorous animals to help"},{"d":"पित्रा","m":"by father"},{"d":"त्यक्तम्","m":"forsaken"},{"d":"वनालयम्","m":"forest as asylum"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"समर्थम्","m":"capable"},{"d":"केन","m":"by what"},{"d":"मन्यसे","m":"reason."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"रक्षसामीश्वरंमांचदेवानांचभयङ्करम् ।हीनंमांमन्यसेकेनह्यहीनंसर्वविक्रमैः","trans":"\"The Lord of Rakshasas is a terror to all including the Devas and am endowed with all kinds of prowess and efficiency. Why do you think I am deficient?\"","words":[{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"ईश्वरम्","m":"Lord"},{"d":"देवानांच","m":"including Devas"},{"d":"भयङ्करम्","m":"fearfulterror"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"सर्वविक्रमैः","m":"all kinds of prowess"},{"d":"अहीनम्","m":"not deficient"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"हीनम्","m":"deficient"},{"d":"केन","m":"why"},{"d":"मन्यसे","m":"think."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"वीरद्वेषेणवाशङ्केपक्षपातेनवारिपोः ।त्वयाहंपरुषाण्युक्तःपरप्रोत्साहनेनवा","trans":"\"I suspect that out of hatred towards me, you are speaking such harsh words to a hero encouraged by the enemy.\"","words":[{"d":"वीरद्वेषेण","m":"out of hatred to hero"},{"d":"रिपोः","m":"enemy"},{"d":"पक्षपातेन","m":"out of one sided view"},{"d":"पर","m":"others"},{"d":"प्रोत्साहनेनवा","m":"by the encouragement of"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I am"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by your"},{"d":"परुषाणि","m":"harsh words"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"spoken"},{"d":"शङ्के","m":"suspect."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"प्रभवन्तंपदस्थंहिपरुषंकोऽभिभाषते ।पण्डितश्शास्त्रतत्त्वज्ञोविनाप्रोत्साहनाद्रिपोः","trans":"\"Which person who has learned the truth of sastras will address such harsh words to one in power without instigation?\"","words":[{"d":"शास्त्रतत्त्वज्ञः","m":"learned in the truth of sastras"},{"d":"पण्डितः","m":"learned"},{"d":"कः","m":"who"},{"d":"विनाप्रोत्साहनाद्रिपोः","m":"without instigation"},{"d":"प्रभवन्तम्","m":"in power"},{"d":"पदस्थम्","m":"address"},{"d":"परुषम्","m":"harsh"},{"d":"अभिभाषते","m":"will speak."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"आनीयचवनासतीतांपद्महीनामिवश्रियम् ।किमर्थंप्रतिदास्यामिराघवस्यभयादहम्","trans":"\"Sita who is like Lakshmi without the lotus has been brought from the forest. Why would I return her for the fear of Rama?\"","words":[{"d":"पद्महीनाम्","m":"without the lotus"},{"d":"श्रियम् इव","m":"like Lakshmi"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"वनात्","m":"from forest"},{"d":"आनीय","m":"brought her"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"राघवस्य","m":"Rama's"},{"d":"भयात्","m":"fear"},{"d":"किमर्थम्","m":"for what"},{"d":"प्रतिदास्यामि","m":"will not return."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"वृतंवानरकोटीभिस्ससुग्रीवंसलक्ष्मणम् ।पश्यकैश्चिदहोभिस्त्वंराघवंनिहतंमया","trans":"\"Indeed, in a short while crores of Vanaras, Sugriva and also Lakshmana and Raghava will be killed by me. Oh!\"","words":[{"d":"कैश्चित्","m":"in short time"},{"d":"अहोभिः","m":"praised"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"निहतम्","m":"killed वानरकोटिभिः crores of Vanaras"},{"d":"वृतम्","m":"surrounding"},{"d":"ससुग्रीवम्","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"सलक्ष्मणम्","m":"and that Lakshmana"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"पश्य","m":"see."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"द्वन्द्वेयस्यनतिष्ठन्तिदैवतान्यपिसंयुगे ।सकस्माद्रावणोयुद्धेभयमाहारयिष्यति","trans":"As even gods will not with stand Ravana in war, of whom Ravana will be afraid of in a duel.","words":[{"d":"दैवतान्यपि","m":"even gods"},{"d":"युद्धे","m":"in war"},{"d":"द्वन्द्वे","m":"duel"},{"d":"नतिष्ठन्ति","m":"not with stand"},{"d":"सः","m":"that he"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"युद्धे","m":"in war"},{"d":"कस्मात्","m":"whom"},{"d":"भयम्","m":"fear"},{"d":"आहारयिष्यति","m":"striking."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"द्विधाभज्येयमप्येवंननमेयंतुकस्यचित् ।एषमेसहजोदोषस्स्वभावोदुरतिक्रमः","trans":"\"I would break my head into two also but not bend my head to anyone. It is my weakness. It is hard to overcome nature.\"","words":[{"d":"द्विधा","m":"into two"},{"d":"भज्येयमपि","m":"resorts to breaks my head"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"also"},{"d":"कस्यचित्","m":"his mind"},{"d":"ननमेयम्","m":"bend myself to any one"},{"d":"एषः","m":"in that way"},{"d":"मे","m":"I"},{"d":"सहजः","m":"natural"},{"d":"दोषः","m":"weakness"},{"d":"स्वभावः","m":"nature"},{"d":"दुरतिक्रमः","m":"to overcome."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"यदितावत्समुद्रेतुसेतुर्बद्धोयदृच्छया ।रामेणविस्मयःकोऽत्रयेवमेभयमागतम्","trans":"\"Rama has constructed a bridge by chance and because of that you are fearing what wonder is there in it?\"","words":[{"d":"रामेण","m":"by Rama"},{"d":"यदृच्छया","m":"by chance"},{"d":"समुद्रे","m":"on the ocean"},{"d":"सेतुः","m":"bridge"},{"d":"बद्धःयदि","m":"constructed तावत् by that"},{"d":"अत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"येन","m":"because of that"},{"d":"मे","m":"to me"},{"d":"भयम्","m":"fear"},{"d":"आगतम्","m":"overtaken"},{"d":"विस्मयः","m":"wonder"},{"d":"कः","m":"what."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"सतुतीर्त्वार्णवंरामस्सहवानरसेनया ।प्रतिजानामितेसत्यंनजीवन्प्रतियास्यति","trans":"\"Rama having crossed the sea with his Vanara army will not go back with life. It is true.\"","words":[{"d":"सःराघवः","m":"that Raghava"},{"d":"वानरसेवयासह","m":"along with Vanara army"},{"d":"आर्णवम्","m":"sea"},{"d":"तीर्त्वा","m":"crossed water"},{"d":"जीवन्","m":"with life"},{"d":"नप्रतियाप्यति","m":"not going back"},{"d":"सत्यम्","m":"true"},{"d":"प्रतिजानामि","m":"will not return back."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"एवंब्रुवाणंसंरब्धंरुष्टंविज्ञायरावणम् ।व्रीळितोमाल्यवान्वाक्यंनोत्तरंप्रत्यपद्यत","trans":"When Ravana was abashed and speaking in that way realizing that he is angry, Malyavan did not reply feeling shy.","words":[{"d":"एवं","m":"in that way"},{"d":"संरब्धम्","m":"abashed"},{"d":"ब्रुवाणम्","m":"speaking"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"to Ravana"},{"d":"रुष्टम्","m":"anger"},{"d":"विज्ञाय","m":"knowing"},{"d":"माल्यवान्","m":"Malyavan"},{"d":"व्रीळितः","m":"feeling shy"},{"d":"उत्तरम्","m":"reply"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"नप्रत्यपद्यत","m":"not uttered."}]},{"v":