"},{"d":"पुत्रम्","m":"son"},{"d":"इन्द्रजितम्","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"व्यादिदेश","m":"assigned duty."}]},{"v":18,"dev":"व्यादिदेशसपूर्वस्यांप्रहस्तंद्वारिराक्षसम् ।दक्षिणस्यांमहावीर्यौमहापार्श्वमहादरौ पश्चिमायामथोद्वारिपुत्रमिन्द्रजितंतदा ।व्यादिदेशमयामायंबहूभीराक्षसैर्भहुभिर्वृतम्","trans":"Ravana posted Prahastha surrounded by many Rakshasas at the east gate, and the Rakshasas of great prowess, Mahaparsva and Mahodara at the southern gate, and like that Mahamaya and Indrajith, his own son at the western gate.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"पूर्वस्यांद्वारि","m":"at the eastern gate"},{"d":"प्रहस्तम्","m":"Prahastha"},{"d":"राक्षसम्","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"व्यादिदेश","m":"posted"},{"d":"दक्षिणस्याम्","m":"at the southern gate"},{"d":"महावीर्यौदि","m":"of great prowess"},{"d":"महापर्श्वा","m":"Mahaparsva महोदरौ Mahodara"},{"d":"व्यादिदेश","m":"posted"},{"d":"अथ","m":"and"},{"d":"तदा","m":"like that"},{"d":"पश्चिमायांद्वारि","m":"at the western gate"},{"d":"महामायाम्","m":"Mahamaya"},{"d":"बहुभिः","m":"many"},{"d":"राक्षसैः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"वृतम्","m":"surrounded by"},{"d":"पुत्रम्","m":"son"},{"d":"इन्द्रजितम्","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"व्यादिदेश","m":"assigned duty."}]},{"v":19,"dev":"उतरस्यांपुरद्वारिव्यादिश्यशुकसारणौ ।स्वयंचात्रगमिष्यामिमन्त्रिणस्तानुवाचह","trans":"Ravana posted Suka and Sarana at the north gate of Lanka and himself reached there and told the ministers that he would be there.","words":[{"d":"उत्तरस्याम्","m":"at the north"},{"d":"पुरद्वारि","m":"of the city gate"},{"d":"शुकसारणौ","m":"Suka and Sarana"},{"d":"व्यादिश्य","m":"posted"},{"d":"स्वयम्","m":"himself"},{"d":"चअत्र","m":"also there"},{"d":"गमिष्यामि","m":"reached"},{"d":"तान्","m":"his"},{"d":"मन्त्रिणः","m":"ministers"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"told."}]},{"v":20,"dev":"राक्षसांतुविरूपाक्षंमहावीर्यपराक्रमम् ।मध्यमेऽस्थापयद्गुल्मेबहुभिस्सहराक्षसैः","trans":"In the middle of the city, he placed Virupaksha, a Rakshasa endowed with extraordinary strength and many more Rakshasas.","words":[{"d":"महावीर्यपराक्रमम्","m":"endowed with extraordinary strength"},{"d":"विरूपाक्षम्","m":"Virupaksha,राक्षसाम् Rakshasa"},{"d":"बहुभिः","m":"and many more"},{"d":"राक्षसैःसह","m":"along with Rakshasas"},{"d":"मध्यमे","m":"middle"},{"d":"गुल्मे","m":"of city"},{"d":"आस्थापयत्","m":"placed."}]},{"v":21,"dev":"एवंविधानंलङ्कायांकृत्वाराक्षसपुङ्गवः ।कृतकृत्यमिवात्मानंमन्यतेकालचोदितः","trans":"The best of Rakshasas under the sway of destiny, having been ordered in that way in Lanka, Ravana felt as though he had accomplished the task.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसपुङ्गवः","m":"best of Rakshasas"},{"d":"लङ्कायाः","m":"in Lanka"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"विधानम्","m":"order"},{"d":"कृत्वा","m":"having done"},{"d":"कालचोदितः","m":"sway of destiny"},{"d":"आत्मानम्","m":"his own"},{"d":"कृतकृत्यमिव","m":"as if accomplished the task"},{"d":"मन्यते","m":"thought."}]},{"v":22,"dev":"विसर्जयामासततस्समन्त्रिणोविधानमाज्ञाप्यपुरस्यपुष्कलम् ।जयाशिषामन्त्रिगणेनपूजितोविवेशचाऽन्तःपुरमृद्धिमन्महत्","trans":"There after making arrangements adequately for the protection of Lanka, taking leave of ministers who offered blessings for his prosperity and uttered words of benediction for his success Ravana entered the inner chambers of the palace. ।। इत्यार्षेवाल्मीकीयेश्रीमद्रामायणेआदिकाव्येयुद्धकाण्डेषटित्रंशस्सर्गः ।। This is the end of the thirty sixth sarga of Yuddha Kanda of the first epic the holy Ramayana composed by sage Valmiki.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"पुरस्य","m":"for Lanka"},{"d":"पुष्कलम्","m":"adequately"},{"d":"विधानम्","m":"arrangements"},{"d":"आज्ञाप्य","m":"having ordered"},{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"मन्त्रिणः","m":"with ministers"},{"d":"विसर्जयामास","m":"taking leave"},{"d":"मन्त्रिगणेव","m":"body of ministers"},{"d":"जयाशिषा","m":"uttering benediction for success"},{"d":"पूजितः","m":"blessing सः him"},{"d":"बुद्धिमत्","m":"with prosperity"},{"d":"महत्","m":"great"},{"d":"अन्तःपुरम्","m":"inner chambers"},{"d":"विवेश","m":"entered."}]}]}